Sentencas: In this study, BaCe0.9Lu0.1O3-alpha was prepared by the sol-gel method with cerium nitrate, lutetium oxide and barium acetate as raw materials and BaCe0.9Lu0.1O3-alpha-NaCl-KCl composite electrolyte was also synthesized using BaCe0.9Lu0.1O3-alpha combined with sodium and potassium chloride.
Titulo: Enhanced Electrochemical Properties of Lu-doped BaCeO3 and KCl-NaCl Composite as Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The samples were characterized by X-ray diffraction (XRD), scanning electron microscopy (SEM) and thermal analyser.
Titulo: Enhanced Electrochemical Properties of Lu-doped BaCeO3 and KCl-NaCl Composite as Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: TGA-DSC plots indicated that a perovskite-type structure was formed above 1040 degrees C.
Titulo: Enhanced Electrochemical Properties of Lu-doped BaCeO3 and KCl-NaCl Composite as Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
